Package com.lopl.melody.audio.handler

Class TrackQueue

java.lang.Object
com.lopl.melody.audio.handler.TrackQueue
All Implemented Interfaces:
TrackScheduler.OnTrackFinished
public class TrackQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements TrackScheduler.OnTrackFinished
This class manages all tracks that are queue to be played. This way no one has to search for a new song if the last one is over. The class has the 'normal' queue, that contains all songs that are queued from the user. The autoQueue contains tracks that are queued by code. i.e. from the AutomaticRequeue.
